name: Lion King
wall: Laem Phra Nang (Railay & Tonsai),Tonsai Bay,Dum's Kitchen
infos: The Lion King has a huge distinctive flake on it. Climb to beneath the flake, and then traverse out right and up the right side of the flake. Steep edges and tricky moves lead to the crux right before the anchor.-4 titanium glue-ins with anchors at the top.
